{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina features views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout includes a living room with kitchen, bedroom, and children's room. The living room has access to a balcony that runs the entire width of the living room, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The apartment is located on the 10th storey, making it the highest positioned and sufficiently illuminated, with orientation towards three cardinal directions (east, southeast, and north). The apartment has a total associated area of 94.93 m2, consisting of an entrance hallway, living room, bedroom, and children's room. The bedrooms are furnished with double beds, nightstands, and wardrobes, while the children's room serves as an office. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet, underfloor electric heating, and a washing machine and dryer. The apartment is equipped with high-quality materials and has been meticulously designed to meet both functional and practical purposes."}
